Teltoli also flaps her wings and dodges the shots, wincing as one 
scraped her ankle. Her wounds were slowing her down, but she clamped 
down on the pain. 

Rage began to build up inside of her until it made her eyes red. Rage 
at this bot that was attacking her. Rage at the evil bots that tried 
to kill her when she first experianced the joys of life once again! 

She snarled and without knowing it, heaved a huge fireball with 
crackling blue energy that was almost two meters in height straight 
at GodFather, sure to hit.
